    <h3>WELCOME TO OUR COMMUNITY</h3>
    <p>You are now part of a community that connects fabulous people from all over the world.</p>
    <p>Move-in, make new friends and discover the city of Hamburg.</p>

    <p style="color: red;">Please read the following carefully, as it includes all information needed for your stay with us!</p>

    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">What do I need to bring?</p>
    <p>All our suites are move-in ready! You only need to bring your suitcase & towels. We will take care of the rest.</p>

    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">Which basic supplies are included?</p>
    <p>Here is a list of basic suppliles, which STACEY provides for you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Washing agent</li>
      <li>Hand soap</li>
      <li>Kitchen paper</li>
      <li>Toilet paper</li>
      <li>Coffee capsules</li>
      <li>Dish detergent</li>
      <li>Dishwasher tabs</li>
      <li>Trash bags</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">Where are my keys?</p>
    <p>We use Kiwi as the Smart Lock solution for all doors. To get started:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Open the Kiwi message in your e-mail inbox</li>
      <li>Sign in</li>
      <li>Now you can open all doors with your mobile phone</li>
    </ul>

    <p>In your room you will find a KIWI chip, which you can also use. At the front doors you can hold it against the nameplate, on the handle in front of the sensor.</p>
