    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">What about the weekly cleaning?</p>
    <p>Our cleaning team will clean your Suite on a weekly basis. Please ask your roommates, if it takes place on Monday or Thursday.</p>
    <p>To ensure an optimal cleaning experience, here is our suggestion:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Remove your stuff from the floor, tables, etc. and store it inside the wardrobe or on your bed</li>
    </ol>

    <p>Our cleaners will clean all spaces, which are made available to them.
    The cleaning of the Common Space will take place 2x a week (Monday & Thursday)</p>

    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">How do I communicate with you?</p>
    <p>Slack is the communication platform for the entire community</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the Slack message in your e-mail inbox</li>
      <li>Sign in</li>
      <li>Now you can communicate with us (STACEY Team) and all other members</li>
    </ol>

    <p style="text-decoration: underline;">#mühlenkamp-general</p>
    <p>All general information concerning recent topics within the location are exchanged here</p>
    <p style="text-decoration: underline;">#mühlenkamp-refill</p>
    <p>We offer a range of "Basic Supplies" You will find these on the shelf inside the common area. If anything is empty, please ask here for a refill</p>
    <p style="text-decoration: underline;">#mühlenkamp-passwords</p>
    <p>All passwords (Internet, etc.)</p>

    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">How does the heating work?</p>
    <p>There are night storage heaters in your room and the common spaces. Please note that these heat up in the evening and the temperature cannot be regulated during the day.</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Temperature can be set directly on the heater</li>
      <li>Wall mounted thermostat only operates the ventilation</li>
    </ol>
